+/* tawc instrumentation: trace which gating predicate inside
+ * present_check_flip() forces a copy-mode present. Compiled in
+ * unconditionally (Xwayland's ErrorF() goes to stderr → captured by
+ * the compositor's logcat tag). The cost is one printf per Present —
+ * negligible vs the actual present pipeline, and the data is the
+ * load-bearing diagnostic for "is the EGL-X11 path picking flip?".
+ *
